  "body": "### Component\n\nForge\n\n### Describe the feature you would like\n\nToken in Solidity are also of 1e18 decimals, which is difficult to recognize when showing in \"%d\" format. I'd like to have \"%e/%x/%X\" supported to see these numbers in exponential/hexdecimal formats.\r\n\r\n\r\n\n\n### Additional context\n\nAlso I'm willing to implement and PR this feat myself. But I do not find where related features are located in the code...So maybe some help to guide me there can also be good!",
